<span id="freeTextContainer17633020630379337735">* Riveting beginning with fantastic scenes of horror <br/>* An uneven middle that I&apos;d love to do all kinds of unholy surgery to, especially the over-emphasis on the uninteresting and rather tedious romance(s)<br/>* But saved by a great premise, awesomely freakish moments, solid writing, and a bang-up, untraditional ending. <br/><br/>Author to watch! Review to come. </span>
  <span id="freeText17633020630379337735" style="display:none">* Riveting beginning with fantastic scenes of horror <br />* An uneven middle that I'd love to do all kinds of unholy surgery to, especially the over-emphasis on the uninteresting and rather tedious romance(s)<br />* But saved by a great premise, awesomely freakish moments, solid writing, and a bang-up, untraditional ending. <br /><br />Author to watch! Review to come. </span>
